Package com.st.st25sdk.type4a.m24srtahighdensity Description

Defines all Tags classes to handle M24SR series The M24SR series are an NFC Forum Type 4 Tags; Tags communicate using the ISO/IEC 14443 Type A protocol. M24SR series belongs to the ST25 family which includes all STMicroelectronics NFC/RFID tag and reader products.
